<h4><a href="https://appleinsider.com/articles/20/08/05/leak-claims-iphone-12-will-use-magnets-to-simplify-charging-positioning">iPhone 12 或采用磁吸充电系统</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356848" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/EelqBaoUEAArtcv.png" alt="" width="706" height="449" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/EelqBaoUEAArtcv.png 706w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/EelqBaoUEAArtcv-360x229.png 360w" sizes="(max-width: 706px) 100vw, 706px" /></p>
<p>Appleinsider 援引 EverythingApplePro 的爆料信息称，声称为 iPhone 12 的机身中加入磁吸充电系统。随后，他们又分享了一张疑似是官方手机壳的图片，内部同样有相关设计。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356884" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/EenybNwUcAAcX1v_meitu_1.jpg" alt="" width="2331" height="1283" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/EenybNwUcAAcX1v_meitu_1.jpg 2331w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/EenybNwUcAAcX1v_meitu_1-360x198.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/EenybNwUcAAcX1v_meitu_1-768x423.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/EenybNwUcAAcX1v_meitu_1-1024x564.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2331px) 100vw, 2331px" /></p>
<p>据分析，这可能意味着 iPhone 12 或是其手机壳会支持反向充电。这个设计也可能让 iPhone 12 在搭配无线充电器使用时，减少了将无线充电模块对准充电器特定位置的麻烦，就和现在的 Apple Watch 一样，一放在充电器上就自动吸到最合适的位置。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.ifanr.com/1356727">三星发布 Galaxy Note20</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356849" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC09680-1.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="405" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC09680-1.jpg 720w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC09680-1-360x203.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></p>
<p>昨晚，三星发布了 Galaxy Note20，有标准版和 Ultra 两种版本。</p>
<p>Note20 采用了 6.7 英寸 FHD 屏幕，存储组合为 8+256GB，并配有 6400 万长焦 + 1200 万广角 + 1200 万超广角的后置三摄组合，支持 30 倍变焦拍照。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356850" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jsiwde-1.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="405" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jsiwde-1.jpg 720w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jsiwde-1-360x203.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></p>
<p>Note20 Ultra 的屏幕则提升至 6.9 英寸，并支持 2K 分辨率和 120Hz 刷新率，存储组合为 12+256GB，后置主摄则为 1.08 亿像素，支持 50 倍变焦拍照和最高 8K 分辨率、120fps 的视频录制。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2020/07/watch-3d-video-reveal-how-sperm-really-swim?utm_source=Nature+Briefing&amp;utm_campaign=c694d7cff4-briefing-dy-20200804&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_term=0_c9dfd39373-c694d7cff4-44846481">精子「游泳」的方式比蝌蚪复杂多了</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356851" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/sperm.gif" alt="" width="666" height="367" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/sperm.gif 666w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/sperm-360x198.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 666px) 100vw, 666px" /></p>
<p>《科学》援引《科学精进》报道指，研究人员最近将人类精子放在 3D 显微镜和高速相机下，平均每秒可记录精子 20-30 个游动的动作。以前在 2D 视觉下，研究人员认为精子的移动方式就像蝌蚪游动一样，呈对称状态。在 3D 视觉下，我们能看到细胞事实上是以侧偏的方式移动。</p>
<p>对精子移动模式的进一步了解，有助于未来生殖治疗的发展。</p>
